page.title: 08TOURISM.
page.content:
ETHEROW COUNTRY PARK:
Etherow Country Park covers most of Compstall. In Summer it gets a lot of tourists coming from all over Britain.there are a lot of different kinds of water birds there like Canada Geese, Mallard and Moor Hens. There are millions of trees and many different types. By the entrance there is a cafe. Different sports go on there like sailing, fishing, model boating and walking. There is a large waterfall and a picnic area nearby.there are other picnic areas and the nicest is one called Sunny Corner. if you look carefully you will be able to see many different types of animals.
